  "detailed_description": "<h1>Upcoming</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >——画面风格——</h2>3D画面，Q版画风，清新氛围，国风场景，尽力还原出我们内心的一片仙山净土。隐逸世外的仙山，宁静祥和的村落，迷离恍惚的幻境，妖异邪诡的佛窟，幻彩斑斓的水底迷宫……<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783810/extras/5927067c95808fec86b76ea26049251e.poster.avif?t=1712751240\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783810/extras/5927067c95808fec86b76ea26049251e.webm?t=1712751240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783810/extras/5927067c95808fec86b76ea26049251e.mp4?t=1712751240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >——战斗模式——</h2>游戏采用即时战斗，冷静的面对Boss的每一次进攻，通过走位和闪避寻找反击的时机，利用技能和背击造成大量伤害。风格迥异各有千秋的boss，在李朔的面前，也都不过尔尔。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783810/extras/1390c37f65958a385cb8b9d7257bd278.poster.avif?t=1712751240\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783810/extras/1390c37f65958a385cb8b9d7257bd278.webm?t=1712751240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783810/extras/1390c37f65958a385cb8b9d7257bd278.mp4?t=1712751240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >——关卡设计——</h2>奇门八卦，五行遁甲。这些仙侠中必不可少的要素，让我们再次回到那个仙侠的幻梦之中。八卦秘境中的泽水困、风地观、天山遁、火雷筮盍，六识错乱的佛门障景等等，体味仙侠世界的机巧奇术。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783810/extras/f0adc246d773276c42209c36f765dbd1.poster.avif?t=1712751240\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783810/extras/f0adc246d773276c42209c36f765dbd1.webm?t=1712751240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783810/extras/f0adc246d773276c42209c36f765dbd1.mp4?t=1712751240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >——探索要素——</h2>丰富的支线和隐藏要素，尽情享受RPG游戏的探索乐趣吧，神秘的儿歌究竟在何处，隐世的酒鬼暗藏什么玄机，波澜不兴的湖面之下，又酝酿着怎样的风波？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783810/extras/4c0817713593c4c68d55fa8c6fca8db1.poster.avif?t=1712751240\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783810/extras/4c0817713593c4c68d55fa8c6fca8db1.webm?t=1712751240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783810/extras/4c0817713593c4c68d55fa8c6fca8db1.mp4?t=1712751240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >——修行法宝——</h2>仙道修行，怎么能少了法器相助，收集神秘法器，从来都是修仙者的梦想。毕竟，法器多的人，都不会活得太惨。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783810/extras/2408439329409f38b32ca107b19180e3.poster.avif?t=1712751240\" width=628 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783810/extras/2408439329409f38b32ca107b19180e3.webm?t=1712751240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783810/extras/2408439329409f38b32ca107b19180e3.mp4?t=1712751240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >——剧情设定——</h2>在这个世界上，无数的修行门派并立，主角所在的三清山，更是道门正道翘楚，然而生性顽劣的主角，每天过着耍耍剑玩，偷偷酒喝的日子。反正天大的事情，也有亲爱的师傅和师兄顶着。却从来没想到，好日子这么快就到了头。<br>九鼎丹书、化神书这些主角听都没听过的名字，又怎么会想到一段风波旅途，就此拉开了序幕。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >——特别说明——</h2>　　《牧剑：化神书》是九鼎工作室对于于国产仙侠题材的RPG游戏的第一次尝试，也是《牧剑》系列的第一作，尝试着让剧情不再围绕着爱情，战斗不再受制于回合，关卡不再局限于迷宫。在仙侠单机游戏的在情怀之外，RPG内核的情理之中，寻找一个属于《牧剑》系列的平衡。<br><br>　　中国的游戏人，始终都有一种特殊的仙侠情怀。过往无数的游戏，无不证明了这一题材在中国玩家心中的特殊地位。一种道与侠的东方精神内核，总有一天，游戏会将这种精神传递到全世界。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >——联系方式——</h2>　　官方QQ群：75289222",
